Class Summary
BoxArtifact This abstract class specialize an UMLArtifact in a box shape based artifact
ClassArtifact This class is an artifact used to represent a class.
ClassPartArtifact This abstract class represent a part of a ClassArtifact
ClassPartAttributesArtifact This class represent the middle Part of a ClassArtifact It can hold an attribute list
ClassPartMethodsArtifact This class represent the lower Part of a ClassArtifact It can hold a method list
ClassPartNameArtifact This class represent the upper Part of a ClassArtifact It can hold a name and a stereotype
LinkArtifact This abstract class specialize an UMLArtifact in a link type artifact
LinkClassRelationArtifact This artifact represent the link between a class and a class relation
LinkNoteArtifact This artifact represent a specific link between a note and any uml artifact
NoteArtifact This artifact represent a note
RelationLinkAggregationArtifact This artifact represent an aggregation relation between two classes
RelationLinkArtifact This abstract class represents any relation artifact between two classes
RelationLinkAssociationArtifact This artifact represent an association relation between two classes
RelationLinkCompositionArtifact This artifact represent a composition relation between two classes
RelationLinkDependencyArtifact This artifact represent a dependency relation between two classes
RelationLinkGeneralizationArtifact This artifact represent a generalization relation between two classes
RelationLinkRealizationArtifact This artifact represent a realization relation between two classes
UMLArtifact This abstract class represent any uml artifact that can be displayed An artifact is something between the graphical object and the uml component.
